creator: matchlessapps
descriptionHtml:
• This, Age Calculator app provides with an easy-to-use interface to the user, irrespective of any age group.
• You just need to choose your exact date of birth (day, month & year) from the provided calendar to get to know your exact age in detail including years, months, days, hours, minutes & seconds to date and information about upcoming birthdays for at least 10 years.
• This, Age Calculator app even provides you with notification to your next/ upcoming birthday.
• You can add friends & family members in the app by providing their date of birth. You will be notified about their upcoming birthday priory so that you would wish them, surprisingly.
• This, Age Calculator app also provides with an amazing feature of providing your age in connection with other planets including Mercury, Venus, Saturn, Jupiter, Mars, Neptune, Uranus and Pluto, comparing to Planet Earth.
• Another unique feature of this, Age Calculator app is to find out next date and day of the week, upon providing the optional data e.g., any date, day, month & year from the provided calendar.
• If you intend to know your age in total as how many years, months, weeks, days, hours and seconds then this would be proven as best age calculating for you.
• If you are asked the same question everywhere as “What is your exact age?” then this Age Calculator would be a best choice for you. You just need to get this app installed and start exploring its sections which are considered to be featured ones.
• This simple and very use to use Age Calculator app facilitates you to share your exact age, upcoming birthday (up-to 10 years) and time as in minutes and seconds you have lived for till date, with your loves ones including friends, families, and colleagues using any social media platform including Facebook, Instagram, twitter, LinkedIn, Google Plus as well as WhatsApp & email.
• This Age Calculator App is 100% free of any cost.
• We would love to get any feedback, comments, suggestions, facing problems during installation or afterwards as your inputs are highly worthy for us in making this Age Calculator app the best with trending features. Please get us updated!
• Now you can save the special days or the dates of yours & your loved ones including birthdays and anniversaries in this Age Calculator app that has been always a tough job for everyone.
• This Age Calculator app can also be used to find out the difference b/w date and the time till the level of minutes as well as the seconds.
• Please try to keep us rated on Google Play Store so that we would stay motivated and keep you guys entertaining with latest trends.
Features / Functions :
A very easy to use app with simple Graphical User Interface.
• Calculate your exact age in years, months, weeks, days and even in seconds till date.
• Add the birthdays, anniversaries or other special events of your friends, families or the loved ones and get notified earlier for surprise wishes.
• Find out your age on other planets rather than Earth that makes this app enriched with a trendy feature.
• Find out your next birthdays up to 10 years.
• This Age Calculator app is also enabled with the Date & time difference calculating feature.
• You can perform daily date mathematical tasks like addition or the subtraction.
• Share your calculated results with your concerning ones in the form of screenshots or through social media channels.
• Share your age with your loved ones like friends, family etc.
• A wonderful Age Calculator app for everywhere who are interested in date calculations.
• Invite your social circle to this great Age Calculating app.
